{"id": "ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 281, "displayName": {"text": "Chayan", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxNU1qaExUVTl0WlRVek56bFZhV05ETUZkVlpHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Really loved this spot. The drinks are so good, you can actually taste the tea, and it goes perfectly with the fresh milk.\n\nThe space is clean and nicely designed, and the staff were super friendly and welcoming. Service was quick too, which made the whole experience even better.\n\nDefinitely a place I’d come back to whenever I’m craving milk tea!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Really loved this spot. The drinks are so good, you can actually taste the tea, and it goes perfectly with the fresh milk.\n\nThe space is clean and nicely designed, and the staff were super friendly and welcoming. Service was quick too, which made the whole experience even better.\n\nDefinitely a place I’d come back to whenever I’m craving milk tea!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Miu Takeshi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115577607430114981266/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3LNfqUUodVLfysIu-TXZb27ovLHZ3KAMUdJZ_OJvVwI2F9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-01T20:38:06.583232368Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxNU1qaExUVTl0WlRVek56bFZhV05ETUZkVlpHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxNU1qaExUVTl0WlRVek56bFZhV05ETUZkVlpHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c32bb35c65fb41:0x1300bd767bf84671"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kclVGcFphbWRIUW1wSFdtcDZjM0ZuZEZGMU4zYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Trying this new place out, missed some good BOGO deal on Lunar New Year. We got the da-hong-pao tea & osmanthus and lychee lemon tea. Da-hong-pao is more like black tea, not quite as strong to me as earl grey, but more flavorful than Lipton ice tea. (The more affordable choice but didn't wow me). The other seems more special, which is osmanthus  lychee lemon tea. Don't see any lychee bits per se, but it's refreshing and slightly on the sour side like what you expect from lemonade (I recommend for hot days, not cold day like today).", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Trying this new place out, missed some good BOGO deal on Lunar New Year. We got the da-hong-pao tea & osmanthus and lychee lemon tea. Da-hong-pao is more like black tea, not quite as strong to me as earl grey, but more flavorful than Lipton ice tea. (The more affordable choice but didn't wow me). The other seems more special, which is osmanthus  lychee lemon tea. Don't see any lychee bits per se, but it's refreshing and slightly on the sour side like what you expect from lemonade (I recommend for hot days, not cold day like today).", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David Ko", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105484966399838822442/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJ4VPRE8Cqwzi0meZiH3ZJO4c-3LyAwiinQH9PWqZ6x01cFg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-18T22:46:49.032343889Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kclVGcFphbWRIUW1wSFdtcDZjM0ZuZEZGMU4zYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kclVGcFphbWRIUW1wSFdtcDZjM0ZuZEZGMU4zYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c32bb35c65fb41:0x1300bd767bf84671"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrMlIyRkVkekJ2WVdoQlFtVkNiRGxpUVRjNFNtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had to check this spot out after hearing it was opened so my wife and I visited on a busy weekend afternoon but our drinks came out really quick.\n\nFirst impressions is that they have two self ordering kiosks. Already a HUGE plus. Space is pretty standard for a grab and go combo with hangout spot. Couple of tables inside and all pretty spacious. Very clean as well which is a nice plus. I love the subtle light green deco all around the shop, which gave of chill vibes overall.\n\nParking - Free in a large outdoor parking lot. Some spots can be a bit tight so watch out for that.\n\nOne thing I always look at when I visit new tea shops are their cups. Chayan has great cups, sturdy, cute yet simple design, and easy to hold. It's also pretty unique compared to other shops when you think about it.\n\n-- WHAT WE ORDERD --\n\n-- Peach Oolong Milk Tea -- ($6.29)\n- This might be the perfect drink on a HOT DAY. It's refreshing, not too overpowering when it comes to the peach. Very standard and to the point. Very easy to sip and finish within seconds!\n\n-- Black Tea Frappe -- ($6.89)\n- Love this drink. It comes with an option to add Pecan nuts on top of your whipped cream thats above some fresh milk tea. Made the drink very creamy but also very savory to a sense. Refreshing and perfect on a hot day. It's also one of their most popular options, highly recommend.\n\nOverall, a wonderful tea spot addition to SoCal. Loved the vibes here and it's certainly one of my go to tea places now whenever I'm in Rowland. With similar vibes to Molly Tea when it comes to quality, I'm excited to visit again to try other drink options. They do seem to have BOGO promotions along with other promotions often as well which is nice.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had to check this spot out after hearing it was opened so my wife and I visited on a busy weekend afternoon but our drinks came out really quick.\n\nFirst impressions is that they have two self ordering kiosks. Already a HUGE plus. Space is pretty standard for a grab and go combo with hangout spot. Couple of tables inside and all pretty spacious. Very clean as well which is a nice plus. I love the subtle light green deco all around the shop, which gave of chill vibes overall.\n\nParking - Free in a large outdoor parking lot. Some spots can be a bit tight so watch out for that.\n\nOne thing I always look at when I visit new tea shops are their cups. Chayan has great cups, sturdy, cute yet simple design, and easy to hold. It's also pretty unique compared to other shops when you think about it.\n\n-- WHAT WE ORDERD --\n\n-- Peach Oolong Milk Tea -- ($6.29)\n- This might be the perfect drink on a HOT DAY. It's refreshing, not too overpowering when it comes to the peach. Very standard and to the point. Very easy to sip and finish within seconds!\n\n-- Black Tea Frappe -- ($6.89)\n- Love this drink. It comes with an option to add Pecan nuts on top of your whipped cream thats above some fresh milk tea. Made the drink very creamy but also very savory to a sense. Refreshing and perfect on a hot day. It's also one of their most popular options, highly recommend.\n\nOverall, a wonderful tea spot addition to SoCal. Loved the vibes here and it's certainly one of my go to tea places now whenever I'm in Rowland. With similar vibes to Molly Tea when it comes to quality, I'm excited to visit again to try other drink options. They do seem to have BOGO promotions along with other promotions often as well which is nice.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kevin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102328750167324980680/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU8uByaiuI6kB15QC2QrPSwXHiBWTQ5Heq75Wu9TwRBLfonwA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-15T07:04:07.938818489Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrMlIyRkVkekJ2WVdoQlFtVkNiRGxpUVRjNFNtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrMlIyRkVkekJ2WVdoQlFtVkNiRGxpUVRjNFNtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c32bb35c65fb41:0x1300bd767bf84671"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xob2NWTjBlR2RDVmswMVFtVnlZaTF2WW5aSVVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I've been to this place many times and I really like it. It has a very thick tea flavor. They actually prepared a puppy cup for the puppy, with an egg yolk on top! I just love it so much!! The waiters were very friendly. Even though it was already past 9 p.m., they still faced every customer in a very good state. I will recommend it to everyone around me!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I've been to this place many times and I really like it. It has a very thick tea flavor. They actually prepared a puppy cup for the puppy, with an egg yolk on top! I just love it so much!! The waiters were very friendly. Even though it was already past 9 p.m., they still faced every customer in a very good state. I will recommend it to everyone around me!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yijin Wang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116071816223957802842/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWP6xnzn62B48nh4IkcGbJY9LfB-hpbLtO15WMPilYdgLwCmc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-21T05:27:59.800363211Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xob2NWTjBlR2RDVmswMVFtVnlZaTF2WW5aSVVFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xob2NWTjBlR2RDVmswMVFtVnlZaTF2WW5aSVVFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c32bb35c65fb41:0x1300bd767bf84671"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCbGNtWm1WbWRYVW0wM1YwWk9VRVV0YnpKNU5HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had such a great experience at Chayan Rowland Heights!\n\nWe tried the genmaicha milk tea and the da hong pao milk tea, both were rich, flavorful, and perfectly balanced. The shop itself has a modern, chic atmosphere that makes it such a nice place to relax and enjoy your drink.\n\nDefinitely a spot we’ll be coming back to again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had such a great experience at Chayan Rowland Heights!\n\nWe tried the genmaicha milk tea and the da hong pao milk tea, both were rich, flavorful, and perfectly balanced. The shop itself has a modern, chic atmosphere that makes it such a nice place to relax and enjoy your drink.\n\nDefinitely a spot we’ll be coming back to again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Charlene Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109630587919000297417/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGLzppwraLMh-ONjqKgIrmaU2XRCfoDTmHgKfqybdjdThU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-14T02:11:09.506034572Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCbGNtWm1WbWRYVW0wM1YwWk9VRVV0YnpKNU5HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCbGNtWm1WbWRYVW0wM1YwWk9VRVV0YnpKNU5HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c32bb35c65fb41:0x1300bd767bf84671"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJQftlXLMrw4ARcUb4e3a9ABM/photos/AWCwydiDe2luKM5YGdGHQ1T4P-0NrDjYvAtDp-n6XRA3e6nzmooYUFauxSCvXI3b-Nlx24POO29Ka5ADzBW1FppmKrGxAoZo-WN_UPC-CDzXMrUXyi9Oe4_Ldknz8aWclrKXXP8JQEZkt2ezrr-5dqQmBwE1SRcRlQc1qavc-V5GWzva6T48N4LkacTWhFAvi6xHmYi3ehH3Ys8oQ-COb_BW9SQTsljvzbixuhcOoCxMRjk1Xrjbvjbux0GmTj_hSQHevFFVX1-B15x-FcesNLTshKA0HfwWSmTw_uW1o7QTrvIO9K8Cb6OAOo7nSKi1w2xnGsdmmV0CecGWgrpTk0785vxpK1ip6bEeYTElvrMIsIqXjxGCFqYluZmFOE6NfvBwaBXEiSpzmEiqvCIxLqMECS9Gxzs8UiAXJfAMV1NA1